      "term" : "bariatric surgery",
      "definition" : "means weight reduction surgical procedures including\r\ngastrojejunostomy, gastric stapling, vertical banded gastroplasty and\r\ngastrectomy with Roux-en-Y anastomosis."
    } ]
  }, {
